# New Income Project Workflow

This workflow standardizes the creation of high-value assets using our Tech Stack (React, Supabase, AI).

1. **Initialize Project**
   - [ ] Run `npx create-next-app@latest . --typescript --tailwind --eslint`
   - [ ] Install Shadcn/UI: `npx shadcn-ui@latest init`

2. **Connect Backend (Supabase)**
   - [ ] Create project in Supabase Dashboard.
   - [ ] Get URL/Key and save to `.env.local`.
   - [ ] Run `npm install @supabase/supabase-js`.

3. **Integrate AI Core**
   - [ ] Copy [gemini_config.json](file:///C:/Users/daria/.gemini/AXON/scratch/gemini_config.json) to project root.
   - [ ] Install AI SDK (if needed) or use fetch wrapper for Gemini.

4. **Monetization Setup (Day 1)**
   - [ ] Setup Stripe/LemonSqueezy account.
   - [ ] Create simple "Pricing" page component.

5. **Deploy**
   - [ ] Push to GitHub.
   - [ ] Connect to Vercel.
